quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  13,38,Futhi ngempela sathumela izithunywa ngaphambilini kwakho futhi sazenzela ukuthi zibe namakhosikazi nezingane futhi kwakungesikhona okwesithunywa ukuthi size nophawu ngaphandle kwemvume kaMvelinqangi isikhathi nesikhathi (udaba nodaba) kunesimemezelo (sikaMvelinqangi)
  13,39,UMvelinqangi ususa lokho akuthandayo futhi aqinise (lokho akuthandayo) futhi kuyena kunomama wencwadi
  13,40,Futhi noma ngabe siyakukhombisa ingxenye yalokho esibathembisa kona noma senze ukuthi ufe ngakho-ke kuphela umthwalo ophezu kwakhe ukushumayela futhi okwethu ukwehlulela
  13,41,Ngakube ababoni yini ukuthi ngempela thina siyeza emhlabeni siwunciphise emaceleni na? UMvelinqangi uyehlulela akekho ohoxisa isehlulelo sakhe futhi yena ungosheshayo ekwahluleleni
  13,42,"Futhi benza icebo labo ababengaphambilini kwabo ngakho-ke angawaMvelinqangi wonke amacebo, uyakwazi konke okusetshenzelwa iyona yonke imiphefumulo futhi abangakholwa bayokwazi ukuthi ingekabani indlu yokugcina"
  13,43,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi, “awusona isithunywa” ithi, “wanele uMvelinqangi njengofakazi phakathi kwami nani nanoma ubani onolwazi lwencwadi.”"